Key Match Events: The match between Morocco and South Africa will take place on January 30, 2024, at 21:00 on beIN Sports 1.
Pre-Game Insights: The Maroccan team is considered favorites, especially after their impressive performance at the World Cup in Qatar, where they lost in the semi-finals against France. They will face South Africa, who they lost to in June 2023 (2-1). The Maroccan team, led by Walid Regragui, is aiming to win the CAN for the first time in 48 years.
